reviewText: I am finishing my collection of Jonny Quest dvd and vhs and this was one that I could not have done without. It was sent fast and I have already viewed it several times.
This cartoon is not anywhere as good as the original series and was really expensive for such a short video. I wish I had not purchased it.

This video was not one of my faviorts but I do like that it tells Jerhima Surde's story and you find out how he got how he is and how he got Quest world. The other deals with ALice stare and it's an ok Ep but I don't much like the eps about Alins.
I LOOOOVVVEEEE it. It's a great Quest
